<H1>Deleting text</H1>

<P>Text is deleted by combining the delete commands 
<STRONG>x</STRONG> and <STRONG>d</STRONG>
with the type of text object to be deleted.</P>

<P>Numbers can also used with both the 
<STRONG>x</STRONG> and <STRONG>d</STRONG> commands
to delete multiple instances of a text object. For example:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>5dw</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This deletes the current word and the following four words.</P>

